        "subject": "LU-1606 api: compile and build lustreapi test",
        "message": "LU-1606 api: compile and build lustreapi test\n\nTo avoid regression of the client api this test checks a simple\nprogram compiles and links. The program is:\n\n    #include <lustre/lustreapi.h>\n    main() {\n      llapi_file_get_stripe(NULL,NULL);\n    }\n\nThe test has been added to the test suite called liblustre.\n\nSigned-off-by: Richard Henwood <rhenwood@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I6038bc984ba7742612dcd1f620304b1f003d66da\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
